                <mxCell id="legend" value="Legend: green = client traffic (POST /orders); solid black = metric/event flow (PutMetricData, auto-extract, SNS publish); blue dashed = telemetry (agent tails, queries, visualization); red = alarm-driven path (p90 breach → SNS).&amp;nbsp;&lt;div&gt;Two custom-metric techniques share the same EC2: EMF writes JSON to a tailed file; PutMetricData calls straight into CloudWatch Metrics. Both feed the same dashboard, and the p90 alarm watches EMF.&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#F5F5F5;strokeColor=#B3B3B3;fontSize=12;align=left;spacingLeft=8;verticalAlign=middle;" parent="1" vertex="1">
